<refsection condition='ref.description'>
<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>GlossDiv</tag> is a section of a <tag>Glossary</tag>. A Glossary
might be divided into sections in order to group terms, perhaps
alphabetically.
</para>

<para>A Glossary may
contain any number of <tag>GlossEntry</tag> or <tag>GlossDiv</tag>
elements, but it cannot
contain a mixture of both at the same level. 
</para>

